# Error Tracking (Optional)
SENTRY_DSN=your_sentry_dsn_here

# =================================
# PRODUCTION DEPLOYMENT NOTES
# =================================

# For production deployment:
# 1. Replace all placeholder values with actual credentials
# 2. Set NODE_ENV=production
# 3. Update NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL to your production domain
# 4. Ensure all Supabase keys are from your production project
# 5. Run `npm run test:ci` to validate configuration
# 
# Environment validation is performed at startup.
# Missing required variables will prevent the application from starting.
#
# For security:
# - Never commit actual credentials to version control
# - Use your deployment platform's environment variable management
# - Rotate keys regularly in production 